Client
  │
  │  POST /student
  ▼
API Controller
  │
  │ 1. Validate input
  │
  │ 2. Save to MongoDB
  ▼
MongoDB
  │
  │ 3. Success
  ▼
Redis
  │
  │ 4. INCR students:version
  │     (e.g. 5 → 6)
  ▼
Response → Client




Client
  │
  │  GET /students
  ▼
API Controller
  │
  │ 1. GET students:version
  │     (e.g. version = 6)
  │
  │ 2. Build cache key
  │     students:list:v6:page:1
  │
  ▼
Redis
  │
  │ 3. Cache HIT?
  │     ├─ YES → return data ✅
  │     └─ NO
  ▼
MongoDB
  │
  │ 4. Fetch users
  ▼
Redis
  │
  │ 5. SET students:list:v6:page:1
  │     (TTL = 60s)
  ▼
Response → Client
